& \therefore i_{C}=\left(\frac{\beta}{\beta+1}\right) i_{E}
\end{aligned}$$

But we know: $\quad i_{C}=\alpha i_{E}$
Therefore, $\quad \alpha=\frac{\beta}{\beta+1}$
or, $\quad \beta=\frac{\alpha}{1-\alpha}$

